The Beats Saigon is turning 9 year old 

Come and celebrate our 9th year anniversary of promoting underground music events in Saigon. After close to 1 decade we are still going strong and loving every minute of presenting local and international artists to this city.

This year we are inviting one of the best turntablists in the world, D-STYLES to perform at the event. 
